      "readme": "This is DSW representation of results of [DATAREX](https://elixir-europe.org/internal-projects/commissioned-services/datarex) F2F event in Bari 24-26 March 2025.\n\nJust a list of indicators with description and maturity levels  but without links to guidelines.\n\nAuthors in alphabetical order:\nMinna Ahokas\nFederico Bianchini\nKorbinian Bösl\nAlessandro Cestaro\nFlora D'Anna\nVilém Děd\nNazeefa Fatima\nNiclas Jareborg\nMijke Jetten\nLuka Kranjc\nBrane Leskošek\nFlavio Licciulli\nAída Moure Fernández\nIvan Mičetić\nMinna Ahokas\nAnna Niehues\nXenia Perez Sitja\nDiana Pilvar\nGil Poiares-Oliveira\nMarina Popleteeva\nAmir Szitenberg\nJeanne Wilbrandt\n\n",
